                <h1>Unlocking Minds: BCI Innovations in Utah</h1>
                <p>BCI Utah, or the Brain-Computer Interface initiative in Utah, focuses on innovative technology that enables direct communication between the brain and external devices. This cutting-edge research seeks to enhance human potential, assist in rehabilitation, and improve quality of life for individuals with disabilities.</p>
